# CHANGELOG

## v3.0.0-beta3 - 2025-06-27

### Added

- Complete Valencian (Valenci√†) translation.
- Form iDevice: Slideshow mode and Check capitalization options.
- Transitions when collapsing/expanding feedback contents and boxes.
